{
  "video_id": "cgxZ4H3gJ8c",
  "title": "You owe it to yourself to experience a total solar eclipse | David Baron",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14280.0,
      "end_time": 17329.0,
      "text": "Before I get to bulk of what I have to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17353.0,
      "end_time": 20913.0,
      "text": "I feel compelled just to mention a couple of things about myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21564.0,
      "end_time": 24613.0,
      "text": "I am not some mystical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24637.0,
      "end_time": 26475.0,
      "text": "spiritual sort of person."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27488.0,
      "end_time": 29516.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a science writer."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29540.0,
      "end_time": 31811.0,
      "text": "I studied physics in college."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31835.0,
      "end_time": 34797.0,
      "text": "I used to be a science correspondent for NPR."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35893.0,
      "end_time": 37427.0,
      "text": "OK, that said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38372.0,
      "end_time": 41611.0,
      "text": "in the course of working on a story for NPR,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41635.0,
      "end_time": 43913.0,
      "text": "I got some advice from an astronomer"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43937.0,
      "end_time": 46440.0,
      "text": "that challenged my outlook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46680.0,
      "end_time": 48650.0,
      "text": "and frankly, changed my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49120.0,
      "end_time": 51204.0,
      "text": "You see, the story was about an eclipse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51228.0,
      "end_time": 55772.0,
      "text": "a partial solar eclipse that was set to cross the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55796.0,
      "end_time": 57628.0,
      "text": "in May of 1994."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58171.0,
      "end_time": 60635.0,
      "text": "And the astronomer -- I interviewed him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60659.0,
      "end_time": 63936.0,
      "text": "and he explained what was going to happen and how to view it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63960.0,
      "end_time": 69181.0,
      "text": "but he emphasized that, as interesting as a partial solar eclipse is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69205.0,
      "end_time": 73715.0,
      "text": "a much rarer total solar eclipse is completely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74319.0,
      "end_time": 77593.0,
      "text": "In a total eclipse, for all of two or three minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77617.0,
      "end_time": 80948.0,
      "text": "the moon completely blocks the face of the sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80972.0,
      "end_time": 86211.0,
      "text": "creating what he described as the most awe-inspiring spectacle"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86236.0,
      "end_time": 87632.0,
      "text": "in all of nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88580.0,
      "end_time": 90789.0,
      "text": "And so the advice he gave me was this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91907.0,
      "end_time": 94904.0,
      "text": "\"Before you die,\" he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94928.0,
      "end_time": 99205.0,
      "text": "\"you owe it to yourself to experience a total solar eclipse.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99925.0,
      "end_time": 102405.0,
      "text": "Well honestly, I felt a little uncomfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102430.0,
      "end_time": 104838.0,
      "text": "hearing that from someone I didn&#39;t know very well;"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104862.0,
      "end_time": 106253.0,
      "text": "it felt sort of intimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106277.0,
      "end_time": 110800.0,
      "text": "But it got my attention, and so I did some research."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110825.0,
      "end_time": 112872.0,
      "text": "Now the thing about total eclipses is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112896.0,
      "end_time": 115282.0,
      "text": "if you wait for one to come to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115306.0,
      "end_time": 118698.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to be waiting a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118722.0,
      "end_time": 123241.0,
      "text": "Any given point on earth experiences a total eclipse"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123266.0,
      "end_time": 126322.0,
      "text": "about once every 400 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127244.0,
      "end_time": 130746.0,
      "text": "But if you&#39;re willing to travel, you don&#39;t have to wait that long."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130770.00000000001,
      "end_time": 135870.0,
      "text": "And so I learned that a few years later, in 1998,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 135111.0,
      "end_time": 137898.0,
      "text": "a total eclipse was going to cross the Caribbean."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 139210.0,
      "end_time": 142549.0,
      "text": "Now, a total eclipse is visible only along a narrow path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142574.0,
      "end_time": 144254.0,
      "text": "about a hundred miles wide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144278.0,
      "end_time": 146372.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s where the moon&#39;s shadow falls."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146396.0,
      "end_time": 148527.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called the \"path of totality.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148551.0,
      "end_time": 150974.0,
      "text": "And in February 1998,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 150998.0,
      "end_time": 154445.0,
      "text": "the path of totality was going to cross Aruba."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154469.0,
      "end_time": 158785.0,
      "text": "So I talked to my husband, and we thought: February? Aruba?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158809.0,
      "end_time": 160528.0,
      "text": "Sounded like a good idea anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160552.0,
      "end_time": 161624.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161648.0,
      "end_time": 164283.0,
      "text": "So we headed south,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164307.0,
      "end_time": 166779.0,
      "text": "to enjoy the sun and to see what would happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166803.0,
      "end_time": 168618.0,
      "text": "when the sun briefly went away."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169356.0,
      "end_time": 172347.0,
      "text": "Well, the day of the eclipse found us and many other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172371.0,
      "end_time": 174552.0,
      "text": "out behind the Hyatt Regency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174576.0,
      "end_time": 175739.0,
      "text": "on the beach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 175763.0,
      "end_time": 177474.0,
      "text": "waiting for the show to begin."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177498.0,
      "end_time": 180668.0,
      "text": "And we wore eclipse glasses with cardboard frames"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 180693.0,
      "end_time": 184812.0,
      "text": "and really dark lenses that enabled us to look at the sun safely."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185787.0,
      "end_time": 190220.0,
      "text": "A total eclipse begins as a partial eclipse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190460.0,
      "end_time": 193822.0,
      "text": "as the moon very slowly makes its way in front of the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193846.0,
      "end_time": 198740.0,
      "text": "So first it looked the sun had a little notch in its edge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198980.0,
      "end_time": 201219.0,
      "text": "and then that notch grew larger and larger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201243.0,
      "end_time": 203910.0,
      "text": "turning the sun into a crescent."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204640.0,
      "end_time": 207399.0,
      "text": "And it was all very interesting, but I wouldn&#39;t say it was spectacular."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 207423.0,
      "end_time": 209347.0,
      "text": "I mean, the day remained bright."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209371.0,
      "end_time": 212381.0,
      "text": "If I hadn&#39;t known what was going on overhead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 212405.0,
      "end_time": 214818.0,
      "text": "I wouldn&#39;t have noticed anything unusual."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 215872.0,
      "end_time": 220682.0,
      "text": "Well, about 10 minutes before the total solar eclipse was set to begin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 220706.0,
      "end_time": 222497.0,
      "text": "weird things started to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 223754.0,
      "end_time": 225609.0,
      "text": "A cool wind kicked up."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226628.0,
      "end_time": 230541.0,
      "text": "Daylight looked odd, and shadows became very strange;"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230565.0,
      "end_time": 232799.0,
      "text": "they looked bizarrely sharp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232823.0,
      "end_time": 236614.0,
      "text": "as if someone had turned up the contrast knob on the TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 237587.0,
      "end_time": 241453.0,
      "text": "Then I looked offshore, and I noticed running lights on boats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 241478.0,
      "end_time": 244410.0,
      "text": "so clearly it was getting dark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 244650.0,
      "end_time": 245651.0,
      "text": "although I hadn&#39;t realized it."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245675.0,
      "end_time": 247948.0,
      "text": "Well soon, it was obvious it was getting dark."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247972.0,
      "end_time": 250116.0,
      "text": "It felt like my eyesight was failing."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 251600.0,
      "end_time": 252780.0,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252804.0,
      "end_time": 254168.0,
      "text": "the lights went out."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255650.0,
      "end_time": 257288.0,
      "text": "Well, at that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257312.0,
      "end_time": 259929.0,
      "text": "a cheer erupted from the beach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259952.0,
      "end_time": 261845.0,
      "text": "and I took off my eclipse glasses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261870.0,
      "end_time": 264461.0,
      "text": "because at this point during the total eclipse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 264485.0,
      "end_time": 267580.0,
      "text": "it was safe to look at the sun with the naked eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 268185.0,
      "end_time": 270100.0,
      "text": "And I glanced upward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271826.0,
      "end_time": 274636.0,
      "text": "and I was just dumbstruck."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 277361.0,
      "end_time": 282980.0,
      "text": "Now, consider that, at this point, I was in my mid-30s."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 282122.0,
      "end_time": 288735.0,
      "text": "I had lived on earth long enough to know what the sky looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289489.0,
      "end_time": 290640.0,
      "text": "I mean --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 290664.0,
      "end_time": 291746.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 291770.0,
      "end_time": 294864.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d seen blue skies and grey skies"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 294888.0,
      "end_time": 298828.0,
      "text": "and starry skies and angry skies"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 298853.0,
      "end_time": 300961.0,
      "text": "and pink skies at sunrise."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301702.0,
      "end_time": 304766.0,
      "text": "But here was a sky I had never seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 306137.0,
      "end_time": 308413.0,
      "text": "First, there were the colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308437.0,
      "end_time": 311402.0,
      "text": "Up above, it was a deep purple-grey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 311426.0,
      "end_time": 312839.0,
      "text": "like twilight."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 312863.0,
      "end_time": 314573.0,
      "text": "But on the horizon it was orange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 314597.0,
      "end_time": 315897.0,
      "text": "like sunset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315922.0,
      "end_time": 317516.0,
      "text": "360 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 318246.0,
      "end_time": 320888.0,
      "text": "And up above, in the twilight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 320912.0,
      "end_time": 323337.0,
      "text": "bright stars and planets had come out."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 323361.0,
      "end_time": 324962.0,
      "text": "So there was Jupiter"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 324987.0,
      "end_time": 326723.0,
      "text": "and there was Mercury"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 326747.0,
      "end_time": 328200.0,
      "text": "and there was Venus."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 328910.0,
      "end_time": 330925.0,
      "text": "They were all in a line."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 332348.0,
      "end_time": 335302.0,
      "text": "And there, along this line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 336108.0,
      "end_time": 338574.0,
      "text": "was this thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338598.0,
      "end_time": 342122.0,
      "text": "this glorious, bewildering thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 342146.0,
      "end_time": 346897.0,
      "text": "It looked like a wreath woven from silvery thread,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 346921.0,
      "end_time": 350115.0,
      "text": "and it just hung out there in space, shimmering."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 352322.0,
      "end_time": 355962.0,
      "text": "That was the sun&#39;s outer atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 355986.0,
      "end_time": 357795.0,
      "text": "the solar corona."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 357819.0,
      "end_time": 360178.0,
      "text": "And pictures just don&#39;t do it justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 360202.0,
      "end_time": 364735.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just a ring or halo around the sun;"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 364759.0,
      "end_time": 368369.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s finely textured, like it&#39;s made out of strands of silk."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369583.0,
      "end_time": 372840.0,
      "text": "And although it looked nothing like our sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372108.0,
      "end_time": 374362.0,
      "text": "of course, I knew that&#39;s what it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 374386.0,
      "end_time": 378218.0,
      "text": "So there was the sun, and there were the planets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 378242.0,
      "end_time": 382273.0,
      "text": "and I could see how the planets revolve around the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 382297.0,
      "end_time": 385820.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like I had left our solar system"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 385106.0,
      "end_time": 387702.0,
      "text": "and was standing on some alien world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 387726.0,
      "end_time": 389491.0,
      "text": "looking back at creation."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 390599.0,
      "end_time": 392990.0,
      "text": "And for the first time in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 393140.0,
      "end_time": 397360.0,
      "text": "I just felt viscerally connected to the universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 397600.0,
      "end_time": 398681.0,
      "text": "in all of its immensity."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 399927.0,
      "end_time": 401435.0,
      "text": "Time stopped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 402207.0,
      "end_time": 404755.0,
      "text": "or it just kind of felt nonexistent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 404779.0,
      "end_time": 407863.0,
      "text": "and what I beheld with my eyes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 407887.0,
      "end_time": 409372.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t just see it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 410255.0,
      "end_time": 412200.0,
      "text": "it felt like a vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 413678.0,
      "end_time": 416536.0,
      "text": "And I stood there in this nirvana"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 417350.0,
      "end_time": 422986.0,
      "text": "for all of 174 seconds -- less than three minutes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 423100.0,
      "end_time": 425393.0,
      "text": "when all of a sudden, it was over."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 425417.0,
      "end_time": 426768.0,
      "text": "The sun burst out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 426792.0,
      "end_time": 428453.0,
      "text": "the blue sky returned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 428478.0,
      "end_time": 431655.0,
      "text": "the stars and the planets and the corona were gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 431679.0,
      "end_time": 433496.0,
      "text": "The world returned to normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 434393.0,
      "end_time": 436116.0,
      "text": "But I had changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 437439.0,
      "end_time": 440695.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s how I became an umbraphile --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 441401.0,
      "end_time": 442567.0,
      "text": "an eclipse chaser."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 442591.0,
      "end_time": 443600.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 443624.0,
      "end_time": 448294.0,
      "text": "So, this is how I spend my time and hard-earned money."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 448818.0,
      "end_time": 454447.0,
      "text": "Every couple of years, I head off to wherever the moon&#39;s shadow will fall"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 454471.0,
      "end_time": 456861.0,
      "text": "to experience another couple minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 456885.0,
      "end_time": 458344.0,
      "text": "of cosmic bliss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 458369.0,
      "end_time": 460656.0,
      "text": "and to share the experience with others:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 460680.0,
      "end_time": 462687.0,
      "text": "with friends in Australia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 462711.0,
      "end_time": 465264.0,
      "text": "with an entire city in Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 465288.0,
      "end_time": 469626.0,
      "text": "In 1999, in Munich, I joined hundreds of thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 469650.0,
      "end_time": 474411.0,
      "text": "who filled the streets and the rooftops and cheered in unison"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 474435.0,
      "end_time": 476362.0,
      "text": "as the solar corona emerged."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 477539.0,
      "end_time": 479755.0,
      "text": "And over time, I&#39;ve become something else:"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 480318.0,
      "end_time": 482406.0,
      "text": "an eclipse evangelist."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 482936.0,
      "end_time": 484775.0,
      "text": "I see it as my job"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 485557.0,
      "end_time": 490385.0,
      "text": "to pay forward the advice that I received all those years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 491189.0,
      "end_time": 493218.0,
      "text": "And so let me tell you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 494350.0,
      "end_time": 496583.0,
      "text": "before you die,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 496607.0,
      "end_time": 501585.0,
      "text": "you owe it to yourself to experience a total solar eclipse."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 501609.0,
      "end_time": 505489.0,
      "text": "It is the ultimate experience of awe."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 506601.0,
      "end_time": 511184.0,
      "text": "Now, that word, \"awesome,\" has grown so overused"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511208.0,
      "end_time": 513372.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s lost its original meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 513395.0,
      "end_time": 517875.0,
      "text": "True awe, a sense of wonder and insignificance"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 517899.0,
      "end_time": 520429.0,
      "text": "in the face of something enormous and grand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 520453.0,
      "end_time": 521688.0,
      "text": "is rare in our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 522469.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525541.0,
      "text": "But when you experience it, it&#39;s powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 526304.0,
      "end_time": 528659.0,
      "text": "Awe dissolves the ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 528683.0,
      "end_time": 530677.0,
      "text": "It makes us feel connected."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 530701.0,
      "end_time": 533796.0,
      "text": "Indeed, it promotes empathy and generosity."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 534740.0,
      "end_time": 539415.0,
      "text": "Well, there is nothing truly more awesome than a total solar eclipse."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 540317.0,
      "end_time": 542702.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, few Americans have seen one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 542726.0,
      "end_time": 544946.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s been 38 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 544970.0,
      "end_time": 548140.0,
      "text": "since one last touched the continental United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 548164.0,
      "end_time": 552232.0,
      "text": "and 99 years since one last crossed the breadth of the nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 552976.0,
      "end_time": 555543.0,
      "text": "But that is about to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 555567.0,
      "end_time": 557999.0,
      "text": "Over the next 35 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 558674.0,
      "end_time": 562958.0,
      "text": "five total solar eclipses will visit the continental United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 562982.0,
      "end_time": 566117.0,
      "text": "and three of them will be especially grand."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 566966.0,
      "end_time": 571640.0,
      "text": "Six weeks from now, on August 21, 2017 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 571664.0,
      "end_time": 574343.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 574367.0,
      "end_time": 578453.0,
      "text": "the moon&#39;s shadow will race from Oregon to South Carolina."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 579116.0,
      "end_time": 584519.0,
      "text": "April 8, 2024, the moon&#39;s shadow heads north from Texas to Maine."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 584543.0,
      "end_time": 586715.0,
      "text": "In 2045, on August 12,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 586739.0,
      "end_time": 589477.0,
      "text": "the path cuts from California to Florida."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 591278.0,
      "end_time": 592524.0,
      "text": "I say:"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 593493.0,
      "end_time": 596840.0,
      "text": "What if we made these holidays?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 596108.0,
      "end_time": 597314.0,
      "text": "What if we --"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 597338.0,
      "end_time": 598366.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 598390.0,
      "end_time": 602720.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 602960.0,
      "end_time": 607153.0,
      "text": "What if we all stood together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 607177.0,
      "end_time": 609253.0,
      "text": "as many people as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 609277.0,
      "end_time": 611490.0,
      "text": "in the shadow of the moon?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 611730.0,
      "end_time": 616913.0,
      "text": "Just maybe, this shared experience of awe would help heal our divisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 616937.0,
      "end_time": 619833.0,
      "text": "get us to treat each other just a bit more humanely."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 620738.0,
      "end_time": 626564.0,
      "text": "Now, admittedly, some folks consider my evangelizing a little out there;"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 626588.0,
      "end_time": 629165.0,
      "text": "my obsession, eccentric."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 629812.0,
      "end_time": 634692.0,
      "text": "I mean, why focus so much attention on something so brief?"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 634716.0,
      "end_time": 638418.0,
      "text": "Why cross the globe -- or state lines, for that matter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 638442.0,
      "end_time": 641459.0,
      "text": "for something that lasts three minutes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 642985.0,
      "end_time": 644135.0,
      "text": "As I said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 644726.0,
      "end_time": 646934.0,
      "text": "I am not a spiritual person."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 647826.0,
      "end_time": 650397.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t believe in God."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 650421.0,
      "end_time": 651729.0,
      "text": "I wish I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 652712.0,
      "end_time": 654951.0,
      "text": "But when I think of my own mortality --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 655693.0,
      "end_time": 657398.0,
      "text": "and I do, a lot --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 658791.0,
      "end_time": 662371.0,
      "text": "when I think of everyone I have lost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 662395.0,
      "end_time": 664114.0,
      "text": "my mother in particular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 665598.0,
      "end_time": 667397.0,
      "text": "what soothes me"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 667422.0,
      "end_time": 670514.0,
      "text": "is that moment of awe I had in Aruba."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 671416.0,
      "end_time": 674532.0,
      "text": "I picture myself on that beach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 674556.0,
      "end_time": 675992.0,
      "text": "looking at that sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 676857.0,
      "end_time": 679290.0,
      "text": "and I remember how I felt."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 680481.0,
      "end_time": 683930.0,
      "text": "My existence may be temporary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 683798.0,
      "end_time": 686305.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s OK because, my gosh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 686329.0,
      "end_time": 688418.0,
      "text": "look at what I&#39;m a part of."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 690340.0,
      "end_time": 692163.0,
      "text": "And so this is a lesson I&#39;ve learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 692187.0,
      "end_time": 694750.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s one that applies to life in general:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 695620.0,
      "end_time": 700250.0,
      "text": "duration of experience does not equal impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 700490.0,
      "end_time": 704550.0,
      "text": "One weekend, one conversation -- hell, one glance --"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 705253.0,
      "end_time": 706708.0,
      "text": "can change everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 708328.0,
      "end_time": 711814.0,
      "text": "Cherish those moments of deep connection with other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 711838.0,
      "end_time": 713248.0,
      "text": "with the natural world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 713273.0,
      "end_time": 715120.0,
      "text": "and make them a priority."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 715360.0,
      "end_time": 717449.0,
      "text": "Yes, I chase eclipses."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 717474.0,
      "end_time": 719491.0,
      "text": "You might chase something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 719515.0,
      "end_time": 722821.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not about the 174 seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 724132.0,
      "end_time": 726819.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about how they change"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 726844.0,
      "end_time": 728411.0,
      "text": "the years that come after."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 728934.0,
      "end_time": 730103.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 730128.0,
      "end_time": 734761.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}